videos.headline: San Diego State WR makes contested, one-handed grab
videos.description: On third-and-seven, Mikah Holder reels in Christian Chapman's pass with a defender on his back for a 22-yard gain and a first down.

videos.headline: Aztecs strike first as Washington pounds it in
videos.description: Juwan Washington takes a handoff at the goal line and powers through the line to score from 1 yard out, giving San Diego State an early 7-0 lead.

videos.headline: San Diego State's Holder makes leaping grab in end zone for TD
videos.description: Christian Chapman throws a jump ball to the end zone and Mikah Holder skies over the defender to make the catch for a 16-yard touchdown, giving the Aztecs a 14-0 lead.

videos.headline: Hawai'i airs it out for 47-yard pickup
videos.description: Dru Brown goes deep, lofting a pass downfield and connecting with Isaiah Bernard for a big 47-yard gain.

videos.headline: Aztec RB drags defender downfield... literally
videos.description: San Diego State RB Rashaad Penny rushes for 12 yards and a first down despite having a Hawai'i defender clinging on to his jersey.

videos.headline: Rainbow Warriors' Barker makes juggling catch on sideline
videos.description: Dru Brown throws to Ammon Barker who bobbles the ball, but tips it to himself and gains possession just before he goes out of bounds for an 11-yard gain.

videos.headline: Brown dives into end zone for Hawai'i TD
videos.description: Rainbow Warriors' QB Dru Brown uses his legs for a touchdown, leaping over the line to score from 1 yard out.

videos.headline: Penny barrels in for San Diego State score
videos.description: Rashaad Penny takes a handoff at the goal line and falls into the end zone for a 1-yard touchdown, giving the Aztecs a 21-7 lead.

videos.headline: Chapman connects with Wells to set up Aztecs at goal line
videos.description: Christian Chapman fools the defense with play-action and finds David Wells over the middle just shy of the goal line for a 30-yard gain.

videos.headline: Penny goes 63 yards untouched for Aztecs TD
videos.description: Rashaad Penny eclipses the 200 rushing yard mark as he scores from 63 yards out and gives San Diego State a 28-7 lead.

videos.headline: Hawai'i picks off Chapman
videos.description: Rainbow Warriors DL Zeno Choi cuts in front of a San Diego State WR and intercepts Christian Chapman's pass.
